00:47:42.360 --> 00:47:45.720
and that center looks after the gross side of life.

00:47:45.920 --> 00:47:48.280
That is how cancer can be cured.

00:47:48.520 --> 00:47:51.400
It's true that Sahaja Yoga has cured cancer

00:47:51.640 --> 00:47:53.440
of so many people and some people in

00:47:53.640 --> 00:47:55.400
ten minutes have got rid of their cancer.

00:47:55.600 --> 00:47:57.840
Ten minutes, is a fact.

00:47:58.040 --> 00:48:01.600
But that doesn't mean that I am going to cure everybody's cancer,

00:48:01.800 --> 00:48:03.920
by any chance. It is not so.

00:48:04.160 --> 00:48:05.800
You see, the trouble with people is,

00:48:06.040 --> 00:48:09.800
they say, "Do you claim you can cure cancer?"

00:48:10.080 --> 00:48:13.560
I say, "I don't claim. But Sahaja Yoga can do it."

00:48:13.800 --> 00:48:15.640
"Then you must cure this cancer."

00:48:15.880 --> 00:48:19.040
I said, "Why? Why should I cure?

00:48:19.320 --> 00:48:21.480
Are you paying Me something?

00:48:21.680 --> 00:48:24.200
Have you called Me here? I have come My own.

00:48:24.440 --> 00:48:27.040
If I want I will; otherwise, I will not."

00:48:27.320 --> 00:48:31.160
You see, it is like a aggression of this kind on a person that,

00:48:31.360 --> 00:48:32.840
"You must show how you can cure."

00:48:33.040 --> 00:48:35.960
Why should I show? I don't want to show it.

00:48:36.240 --> 00:48:39.600
Like I had a very big lecture in the medical college,

00:48:39.840 --> 00:48:41.360
medical institute in India,

00:48:41.560 --> 00:48:43.880
and of course the Vice Chancellor was very much impressed.

00:48:44.080 --> 00:48:46.080
But some of the doctors they came and they said,

00:48:46.320 --> 00:48:48.640
"Mother, we will give you four patients of cancer

00:48:48.880 --> 00:48:49.760
and you cure them."

00:48:49.960 --> 00:48:53.560
I said, "I have no time. I am very busy.

00:48:53.800 --> 00:48:55.600
You better ask them to come to Sahaja Yoga,

00:48:55.800 --> 00:48:57.360
get their realization and cure themselves.

00:48:57.560 --> 00:49:00.800
I have no time for that. I am sorry. I am busy with other work."

00:49:01.040 --> 00:49:02.760
So, then they said, "All right.

00:49:02.960 --> 00:49:05.360
Do you have any file of the patients you've cured?"

00:49:05.560 --> 00:49:09.240
I said, "I have none. I have no time for filing."

00:49:09.520 --> 00:49:12.600
It just flows. It just works. What am I to write down everywhere?

00:49:12.880 --> 00:49:15.520
This is it. I have cured this x, y, z, for what?

00:49:15.800 --> 00:49:18.800
I have no clientele. I do not have to cash it.

00:49:19.000 --> 00:49:20.400
So why should I do it?

00:49:20.640 --> 00:49:22.400
It's just flowing. Those who want to have it,

00:49:22.600 --> 00:49:26.200
can have it and can work it out. But you cannot force Me

00:49:26.440 --> 00:49:29.000
that,  "You must write down and …", for what?

00:49:29.280 --> 00:49:32.880
What is the purpose? I am not running a hospital.

00:49:33.120 --> 00:49:37.200
I don't have to have a credibility on that, if I cure or not.

00:49:37.440 --> 00:49:40.160
For that doctors have to get their realization first.

00:49:40.400 --> 00:49:42.800
If they don't get their realization, I am not bothered.

00:49:43.000 --> 00:49:44.760
If they are really bothered about cancer,

00:49:44.960 --> 00:49:48.040
or any other disease, why don't they take their realization

00:49:48.280 --> 00:49:50.080
and help their patients? They can.

00:49:50.320 --> 00:49:52.480
But the patients who are not interested in God,

00:49:52.680 --> 00:49:54.840
God is also not interested in those patients.

00:49:55.080 --> 00:49:57.920
It's common sense. God has the greatest common sense.

00:49:58.160 --> 00:50:00.720
The lights which are never going to work out,

00:50:00.920 --> 00:50:02.280
which are absolutely useless,

00:50:02.520 --> 00:50:04.800
you are not going to repair them, will you?

00:50:05.160 --> 00:50:06.760
No human being is going to do that.

00:50:06.960 --> 00:50:08.160
What's the use of repairing a light

00:50:08.360 --> 00:50:09.600
which is never going to work out?

00:50:09.800 --> 00:50:13.520
So God is also like that. He has such a lot of common sense.

00:50:13.720 --> 00:50:15.720
He is not going to waste His energy for these things.

00:50:15.920 --> 00:50:20.320
The most important thing today is not to cure people

00:50:20.520 --> 00:50:22.440
but to give them realization;

00:50:22.640 --> 00:50:27.520
to redeem them, to evolve them, is the main part.

00:50:27.720 --> 00:50:31.000
You can be counseled, you can be told, everything explained,

00:50:31.240 --> 00:50:33.240
you can be brought to logically conclusion.

00:50:33.480 --> 00:50:36.320
But the aim is to get your realization

00:50:36.560 --> 00:50:38.640
and not to worry about your illness.

00:50:38.880 --> 00:50:40.680
Illness will disappear gradually.

00:50:40.920 --> 00:50:44.000
It has happened with so many people and it should happen with you.

00:50:44.240 --> 00:50:45.520
But it should not be a condition,

00:50:45.760 --> 00:50:48.240
that you come to Sahaja Yoga as an obligation on us

00:50:48.440 --> 00:50:50.640
that,  "We have come to Sahaja Yoga, you better now."

00:50:50.880 --> 00:50:54.760
That's not so, because, as you know, we have no organization.

00:50:55.000 --> 00:50:56.640
There is no organization that we have.

00:50:56.880 --> 00:50:59.800
You have to come humbly to it, and it works out.

00:51:00.080 --> 00:51:03.560
God is the ocean of compassion, ocean of love.

00:51:03.760 --> 00:51:05.520
He is the one who is so anxious

00:51:05.760 --> 00:51:07.680
that you all should enter into His kingdom

00:51:07.960 --> 00:51:10.560
to occupy your great seats as His children.

00:51:10.800 --> 00:51:13.160
He is the Father of the Fathers.

00:51:13.360 --> 00:51:16.240
He is the most loving Father you could think of.

00:51:16.480 --> 00:51:20.800
Then when we challenge Him like this, He doesn't like it.

00:51:21.080 --> 00:51:24.000
We have to enter into His kingdom in a humble way,

00:51:24.240 --> 00:51:27.280
and He will definitely bestow His blessings on all of you,

00:51:27.480 --> 00:51:29.440
because He is the one who is so anxious.

00:51:29.680 --> 00:51:33.040
I Myself amazed at the way He is blessing people.

00:51:33.320 --> 00:51:36.560
Imagine six thousand people before Me, they just get realization.

00:51:36.800 --> 00:51:38.560
Can you imagine such a thing happening?

00:51:38.760 --> 00:51:40.360
I have seen Myself. It's happening.

00:51:40.560 --> 00:51:42.800
So many things are happening today

00:51:43.000 --> 00:51:45.680
that is evident that God is very gracious,

00:51:45.920 --> 00:51:48.360
as well as He is wrathful.

00:51:48.600 --> 00:51:53.480
He is a wrathful God for people who do not take to Him.

00:51:53.680 --> 00:51:56.600
He is wrathful. And that's why one has to be careful.

00:51:56.800 --> 00:51:59.560
If you lead a life on your own - "What's wrong?"

00:51:59.840 --> 00:52:03.600
"What's wrong" is one of the philosophies people have

00:52:03.880 --> 00:52:08.000
- then you have to pay for it, this way or that way.

00:52:08.280 --> 00:52:11.560
So as a Mother I have to tell you that, "Why not?"

00:52:11.800 --> 00:52:13.360
When you have got everything.

00:52:13.680 --> 00:52:17.360
You have got the spirit within you. Is the power is within you.

00:52:17.640 --> 00:52:20.280
Everything is there. Why not get your realization?

00:52:20.520 --> 00:52:24.320
Why succumb to this useless ego which is not yourself?

00:52:24.600 --> 00:52:29.880
You are not your ego. You are your self. You are your spirit.

00:52:30.080 --> 00:52:32.600
And that spirit, when it comes to your attention,

00:52:32.800 --> 00:52:34.680
you become such a wonderful person.

00:52:34.920 --> 00:52:40.480
The whole thing is lost. Like a lotus rising out of the mud,

00:52:40.720 --> 00:52:43.520
it covers the whole of that pond

00:52:43.760 --> 00:52:46.880
and its fragrance fills the atmosphere with such beauty.

00:52:47.160 --> 00:52:50.600
That's what happens to you when you get it. So why not have that?

00:52:50.800 --> 00:52:54.720
This is your own, within your self, and the Divine is so anxious.

00:52:54.920 --> 00:52:57.240
I don't know what is the missing point.

00:52:57.480 --> 00:52:59.800
Today, I am sorry they have today called Me

00:53:00.160 --> 00:53:02.480
after this program for a radio, and I am going there.

00:53:02.760 --> 00:53:05.320
I don't know how many people are going to attack Me on the phone.

00:53:05.560 --> 00:53:07.360
You see, all kinds of things they say on the phone.

00:53:07.560 --> 00:53:09.400
But I told them I will not receive the phone.

00:53:09.600 --> 00:53:11.040
You better receive the phone and let Me know.

00:53:11.280 --> 00:53:13.040
Because all these things are subject to,

00:53:13.280 --> 00:53:17.440
I find that people use it for just call sometimes,

00:53:17.640 --> 00:53:19.400
for not expressing anything good

00:53:19.640 --> 00:53:21.840
but for expressing something that's

00:53:22.120 --> 00:53:26.400
inside them anti-God, absolutely anti-God thing.

00:53:26.600 --> 00:53:28.520
I hope today they will behave themselves

00:53:28.760 --> 00:53:31.760
and it will be a good time for them

00:53:32.000 --> 00:53:34.080
that they should enjoy the bliss of God.

00:53:34.320 --> 00:53:37.560
I must thank for people who rang Me up to say

00:53:37.760 --> 00:53:42.320
that they received their vibrations on the television.

00:53:42.560 --> 00:53:45.760
And that they telephoned to Me and they found out My phone number,

00:53:45.960 --> 00:53:48.400
because My phone number was not available.

00:53:48.640 --> 00:53:50.840
And it should happen to all of you today,

00:53:51.040 --> 00:53:52.360
that you should get your realization.

00:53:52.560 --> 00:53:55.280
So the first intense feeling should be

00:53:55.480 --> 00:53:58.920
that we should get our realization, somehow we get it,

00:53:59.160 --> 00:54:02.200
and then we will talk about the rest of the things.

