00:54:15.320 --> 00:54:19.560
and then we should go ahead with the procedure of realization.

00:54:19.800 --> 00:54:22.080
But too many questions are not needed.

00:54:22.320 --> 00:54:23.960
What you need is your realization.

00:54:24.200 --> 00:54:25.760
Actually, if you ask too many questions,

00:54:25.960 --> 00:54:27.600
sometimes the realization doesn't work out.

00:54:27.840 --> 00:54:29.640
Not to frighten you but I tell you,

00:54:29.880 --> 00:54:31.200
because your mind starts working.

00:54:31.400 --> 00:54:33.680
You have to, you see, take it beyond your mind.

00:54:33.920 --> 00:54:37.200
Tomorrow I'll tell you about that great chakra of Agnya,

00:54:37.440 --> 00:54:40.000
which is bestowed upon the deity of Jesus Christ.

00:54:40.280 --> 00:54:42.560
That how, when the Kundalini rises through it,

00:54:42.760 --> 00:54:47.280
how He sucks in these two horrible things called ego and superego,

00:54:47.560 --> 00:54:51.280
and how you become thoughtlessly aware and you come in the present.

00:54:51.520 --> 00:54:55.880
And you become, when it comes out of your fontanel bone area,

00:54:56.080 --> 00:54:59.320
the real baptism takes place and you get connected.

00:54:59.640 --> 00:55:01.680
You get connected with the whole

00:55:01.920 --> 00:55:04.360
and you become collectively conscious. You become.

00:55:04.560 --> 00:55:05.760
Again I say, it is actualization.

00:55:05.960 --> 00:55:08.480
It is not just talking that, "We are all brothers and sisters,"

00:55:08.680 --> 00:55:11.560
but you just become it, comes in your awareness.

00:55:11.800 --> 00:55:16.360
And you start feeling the other person on your fingertips,

00:55:16.600 --> 00:55:19.760
yourself, on your fingertips. As Mohammed has said,

00:55:20.000 --> 00:55:23.480
"At the time of resurrection, your hands will speak."

00:55:23.680 --> 00:55:26.800
He has spoken more about this time than about the doomsday.

00:55:27.000 --> 00:55:29.160
But all the Muslims are talking about the doomsday only.

00:55:29.360 --> 00:55:31.880
I don't know why they are waiting for that before this.

00:55:32.080 --> 00:55:33.840
So first the resurrection time has to come

00:55:34.040 --> 00:55:37.560
because in all graciousness and kindness and compassion of God,

00:55:37.800 --> 00:55:40.600
He is going to give us a full chance to achieve ourselves,

00:55:40.840 --> 00:55:44.800
because this is His creation. He is anxious to do it.

